data.description:
Welcome to your dream home at 12006 Stoneridge Gap Lane in Manor, TX! This stunning property offers a perfect blend of modern luxury, comfort, and a tranquil suburban lifestyle. Situated in the desirable Stonewater neighborhood, this home is sure to impress even the most discerning buyers.

As you approach this beautiful residence, you'll be captivated by its charming curb appeal, featuring manicured landscaping and a welcoming front porch. Step inside, and you'll immediately notice the spacious, open-concept living spaces adorned with stylish finishes and an abundance of natural light. The well-appointed kitchen boasts granite countertops, modern appliances, and ample cabinet space, making it a chef's delight.

The primary bedroom suite is a true retreat, complete with a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub and a separate shower. Two additional generously sized bedrooms offer plenty of space for family and guests.

12006 Stoneridge Gap Lane is conveniently located near major highways, shopping, dining, and excellent schools. The community offers a neighborhood park, providing a safe and fun environment for children to play.

Don't miss this opportunity to make this impeccable residence your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience the exceptional lifestyle that 12006 Stoneridge Gap Lane, Manor, TX, has to offer. This is your chance to own a piece of Texas paradise!
